22 emergency supplies and equipment stockpile plan described in ORS 401.111;
23 “(b) Organizations involved in the development, implementation and sustainment of the
24 emergency preparedness equipment grant program described in ORS 401.551; and
25 “(c) Organizations involved in other stockpile or resilience grant programs carried out
26 by state agencies.
27 “(2) The office may take actions as necessary to ensure that supplies, equipment and
