1 “(2) The office is under the supervision and control of a facilitator, who is responsible for
2 the performance of the duties, functions and powers of the office.
3 “(3) The Director of the Department of Public Safety Standards and Training shall ap-
4 point the facilitator, who holds office at the pleasure of the director.
5 “(4) The facilitator shall be paid a salary as provided by law or, if not so provided, as
6 prescribed by the director, with the approval of the Governor.
7 “(5) For purposes of administration, the facilitator may organize and reorganize the of-
