38 “(b) Public safety projects will help to protect natural resources in Oregon, including
39 native fish and wildlife, against natural and man-made disasters; and
40 “(c) Enhancing Oregon’s ability to prepare for and recover from emergencies will in-
41 crease investment, business activity and economic development in this state.
